                                            <div class="va_con _j_master_content" data-cs-t="ginfo_kw_hotel">
    <div class="block-loading loading_backward"></div>
<div class="_j_content_box">
	        <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277385329">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;近一年，与许多同龄人一样，在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10198.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="深圳" target="_blank">深圳</a>带外孙，在这难得的平静日子里，我把之前的欠帐补了一些，分别发出了《环法<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>游游记》和《<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="俄罗斯" target="_blank">俄罗斯</a>漫游游记》。前几日，家兄家嫂携孙女来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10198.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="深圳" target="_blank">深圳</a>探望我们，谈及下一步还准备到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a><a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>游，邀我们一起同游，一是兄弟同游机会难得，二是想让孙辈的小姐弟多一些交流接触的机会；三是刚好旧账告一段落，因而欣然答应，并简单准备一下就出发了。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="277385797" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">行程安排</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277385798">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我们是2017年12月15日从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10198.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="深圳" target="_blank">深圳</a>出发的，12月24日返回<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10198.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="深圳" target="_blank">深圳</a>，来回含路途一共九天，我们的详细行程表和路线图如下。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277385490" data-seq="277385492" data-pid="277385490" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8142058/277385490.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:317px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/7A/85/wKgBEFpE1HeAYAR9AACCrMR37BQ640.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/7A/85/wKgBEFpE1HeAYAR9AACCrMR37BQ640.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277385490" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277385629">
            行程表
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277385491" data-seq="277385493" data-pid="277385491" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8142058/277385491.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:521px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/7A/86/wKgBEFpE1HiABiQHAAN5BF6qCKk521.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/7A/86/wKgBEFpE1HiABiQHAAN5BF6qCKk521.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277385491" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277385643">
            旅游线路图<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我们这一次主要是与家兄一家带着小孙女、小外孙出来转转，一切安排都是围绕着他们，游玩的景点都以小孩的兴趣为主，所以这篇拙作可能对准备到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>亲子游的朋友会有一些帮助；另外由于出行比较仓促，特别是对过海轮渡的情况预计不足，所以将有关琼州海峡轮渡的情况写下来给准备驾车过轮渡的朋友一些最新信息。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="277386088" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">景点风光</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277386089">
            1、海滩<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我们这次到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>玉带滩、神州半岛、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196328.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚湾" target="_blank">三亚湾</a>、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196343.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大东海" target="_blank">大东海</a>等海滩，总的来说，对于2~5岁（甚至更大一些）的小朋友而言，沙滩是他们的最爱，他们可以在沙滩上尽情的玩耍，挖沙、造型、拾贝壳、赶海等等，乐此不疲，兴趣盎然。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不过，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196343.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大东海" target="_blank">大东海</a>海滩范围不大、而且太商业化了，不太适合小朋友玩耍。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>玉带滩是一条自然形成的地形狭长的沙滩半岛，位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>，全长8.5公里，狭长的玉带滩把河水、海水分开，一边是烟波浩瀚的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>，一边是平静如镜的万泉河。<br />
<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277417283" data-seq="277417285" data-pid="277417283" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8142058/277417283.html">
