            <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>玉带滩<br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11616.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="万宁" target="_blank">万宁</a>神州半岛位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11616.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="万宁" target="_blank">万宁</a>市，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/27870.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="东海" target="_blank">东海</a>岸中部，它北倚苍翠六岭，南临浩瀚<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>，海岸平缓，沙滩细软。<br />

        </p>
