            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277425313">
            小朋友对猴子还是很有兴趣的
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277424686" data-seq="277424687" data-pid="277424686" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8142058/277424686.html">
