            <div id="_j_photo_277429245" data-seq="277429246" data-pid="277429245" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8142058/277429245.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/94/24/wKgBEFpE-GqAWHP_AAzVkSHVXqU26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/94/24/wKgBEFpE-GqAWHP_AAzVkSHVXqU26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277429245" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277429294">
            缆车看到的南湾水上人家<br />
<br />
3、潭门渔港<br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;潭门渔港位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>省<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/41342.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="琼海" target="_blank">琼海</a>市潭门镇，它是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>岛最大的渔业远海捕捞集中的重要港口，有一千多年的历史。它是个观赏类景点，小朋友可以跟着大人在户外走走，但没有参与性活动。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277430042" data-seq="277430043" data-pid="277430042" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8142058/277430042.html">
